  VX_IQA_Inter(A,B)/2 = VeeX(A,B)/2
                      = Exchange-Correlation Energy Contribution to E_IQA_Inter(A,B)/2
                      = E_IQA_Inter(A,B)/2 - VC_IQA_Inter(A,B)/2
  Note that:
       Vneen(B,A)/2 = Vneen(A,B)/2
       V_IQA_Inter(B,A)/2 = V_IQA_Inter(A,B)/2
       VC_IQA_Inter(B,A)/2 = VC_IQA_Inter(A,B)/2
       VX_IQA_Inter(B,A)/2 = VX_IQA_Inter(A,B)/2
  Note that, within numerical integration errors, we should have:
       Vneen(A,SumB)/2 = Vneen(A) - Vne(A,A)
       V_IQA_Inter(A,SumB)/2 = V_IQA(A) - V_IQA_Intra(A)
       VC_IQA_Inter(A,SumB)/2 = VC_IQA(A) - VC_IQA_Intra(A)
       VX_IQA_Inter(A,SumB)/2 = VX_IQA(A) - VX_IQA_Intra(A)
See "2EDM Note" and "DFT Note".
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
